{"tid":373770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"“帕卡”將進入南海 本澳最快明掛1號風球","createTime":"2017-08-25T09:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T09:12:11.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"612da14b0b44f9e5d3f6ab147e43920cd01dc37f","tid":373770,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:05:45.000Z","msg":"(澳門電台消息) 氣象局表示，今年第 14個熱帶氣旋於今日 (25日) 清晨正式形成，被命名為&ldquo;帕卡&rdquo;，現已發展成熱帶風暴，正集結在菲律賓以東的洋面上，按照最新的路徑預測，預料 &ldquo;帕卡&rdquo;將橫越呂宋島，明日進入南海，採取西北偏西方向移動，大致趨向廣東沿岸。<br />\n<br />\n氣象局預料&ldquo;帕卡&rdquo;將於星期日 (27日) 中午前後最接近本澳，並於星期日稍後時間在本澳至湛江之間登陸。接照目前的路徑分析，本澳最快於明日發出 1號風球，星期日凌晨至早上頗大機會懸掛 3號風球。<br />\n<br />\n受到&ldquo;帕卡&rdquo;影響，氣象局預料本澳在低窪地區在星期日出現輕微水浸。 (廖冬韻  黃偉鴻)"},{"pid":"83b208d3fee187252d734f070799d7c5fa9b83ca","tid":373770,"uid":25099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:08:04.000Z","msg":"解放軍咪撚走呀, <br />\n築人鍊去擋風啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c6075c60255516b80cd1dd72a9d6222b63a801","tid":373770,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:08:15.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"00deb07c4d9ca26347cd0ba6ee1b641b0bc3bfe2","tid":373770,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>解放軍咪撚走呀, <br />\n築人鍊去擋風啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n摺被起澳門力場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517905ffbfd38b95c0a05cc854516e94afdf418a","tid":373770,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:10:10.000Z","msg":"澳門依家就一直掛10號掛到下星期啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33effe3788c51154267bcf7865e524d2bf164313","tid":373770,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:12:11.000Z","msg":"解放軍準備撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}